title: Did Jared Kouchner go to Saudi Arabia because there was no extradition treaty with the United States?
subtitle: Kochner left for Saudi Arabia on a surprise trip, where the team of Special Advocate Robert Mueller was about to file indictments, causing unfounded speculation.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Jared Kouchner made a surprise trip to Saudi Arabia to avoid being caught in the middle of Mueller's probe.
